Welcome to Regex Finder Items

Since there wasn't a usable Automator action available on Snow Leopard, we decided to create one since we needed it ourselves. Please give it a try, if you have any comments or other feedback you can send an email to info@lsd-ltd.biz.

The description of the Automator action contains a link reference to the ICU website that defines the syntax of the regular expressions.

Enjoy!
